<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé hé huá a nǐ shì wǒ de shén 迦南903</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé hé huá a nǐ shì wǒ de shén,
 yé hé huá a nǐ shì wǒ men de shén.
 wǒ men yī tóng xiàng nǐ jǔ shǒu, yī tóng xiàng nǐ qí dǎo.
 qiú nǐ àn zhe nǐ de shí hòu, bǎ wǒ men de guó jiā lái zhěng jiù.
 dào míng tiān nǎ dào míng tiān,
 wǒ men jiāng huì yī tóng gē chàng. nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì wǒ men de shén.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>903</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>